      "startTime": 185.2000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "優は新しい衣装のアイデアを出したり、最終回用の企画\nを先方に提案したり、本当に頑張ってくれていたからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ you worked really hard‚ coming up with new costume ideas and\nsuggesting ideas for the final episode.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.5427403847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "そういう{user}さんこそ\n頑張ってくれてはったやん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the one who\nworked hard‚ {user}-san~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.1868405188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんから聞いたで。うちのことだけやなくて\n瑠依ちゃんのこともフォローしてくれてはったんやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Rui-chan. You didn’t just look after me‚\nyou also looked after Rui-chan‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.7666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうな。今回、トリエルが前に進めたのは\n{user}さんのおかげや",
      "translations": {
